Welcome Guest

Search the Companies Register

Show Help

To search for an entity type the entity name, number or beginning of the entity name in the field below and then click on the SEARCH button. A list of results that match your search criteria will be displayed. The search results will display whether an entity is registered or has been removed.

To search for a director or shareholder enter the person's surname first followed by their first name. You can search just using a person's first name or their surname; however the results will always display the surname first. A list of results that match your search criteria will be displayed below. The search results will display whether a person is a director or shareholder of a company.

To perform an advanced search click on the Show advanced search link in the top right corner.

Large searches | If your search returns more than 200 search results, refine your search using the advanced search. In some cases you may be able to obtain the full list of results, request the remaining results online.
